# HaloNutraTherapy CRM — User Guide

**Live app:** [hnt-crm.vercel.app](https://hnt-crm.vercel.app)  
**Backend:** Google Sheet (HNT-CRM Master)  
**Last updated:** June 2026

---

## What Is This?

The HNT-CRM is a sales and partnership tracking tool for HaloNutraTherapy. It gives you a single place to manage outreach across three contact segments:

- **Influencers** — podcasters, physicians, and content creators ranked by priority score, NAD alignment, and access
- **White Label** — supplement and wellness brands that could carry or co-market HNT products
- **NAD Dealers** — IV clinics, longevity centers, and wellness chains that administer NAD protocols

Everything you do in the app — updating a status, logging a note, setting a next action — saves automatically to the Google Sheet, so the data is always in sync.

---

## Getting Started

Visit [hnt-crm.vercel.app](https://hnt-crm.vercel.app) in any browser. The app loads your contacts directly from Google Sheets. All 117 contacts will appear within a second or two.

