## Navigating the App

### Sidebar (desktop) / Bottom bar (mobile)
Use the left sidebar on desktop or the icon bar at the bottom on mobile to switch between views:

| Icon | View | What it shows |
|------|------|--------------|
| 📊 | Dashboard | KPI summary, pipeline funnel, recent activity |
| ⭐ | Influencers | All influencer contacts sorted by priority score |
| 🏷️ | White Label | White label partner opportunities |
| 🏥 | NAD Dealers | IV clinics and NAD wellness centers |
| 🔄 | All Contacts | Every contact in one combined pipeline view |

On mobile, tap the **☰ hamburger menu** in the top left to open the full sidebar.

