## Dashboard

The dashboard gives you a quick read on where your pipeline stands.

**KPI Cards**
- **Total Contacts** — all contacts across all three segments
- **Tier 1 Contacts** — highest priority targets (score ≥ 8.5 for influencers, Tier 1 for dealers/white label)
- **Active Outreach** — contacts with status: Contacted, In Discussion, or Proposal Sent
- **Active Partners** — contacts marked as Active Partner

**Pipeline by Stage**
The funnel chart shows how many contacts are at each stage. **Click any bar** to jump directly to the All Contacts view filtered to that stage.

**Recent Activity**
Shows the last 10 status updates and notes logged this session. Use the date range buttons — **7 days / 30 days / 90 days / All time** — above the funnel to adjust the activity window.

