## Working with Contacts

### Searching and Filtering
Each segment view has a search box and filter buttons at the top:
- **Search** — type any part of a name, company, location, or platform
- **Filter buttons** — All / Tier 1 / Tier 2 / Not Contacted (Prospect)
- The sidebar badge updates dynamically — when you filter, it shows `12/46` so you always know how many are visible vs total

### Sorting Columns
Click any **underlined column header** to sort by that column. Click again to reverse the sort direction. A ↑ or ↓ arrow shows the active sort. You can sort by name, tier, score, status, location count, and more.

### Opening a Contact
Click any row to open the contact detail panel on the right. It shows:
- All key data for that contact (scores, links, notes from research)
- Their current pipeline status and activity log

