## Updating a Contact

1. Click a contact row to open the detail panel
2. Change the **Pipeline Status** dropdown to the new stage
3. Fill in **Next Action** — what needs to happen next (e.g. "Send proposal")
4. Set a **Due Date** for that action
5. Add a **note** in the text box describing what happened (call, email, meeting, etc.)
6. Hit **Save Update**

The panel closes, a ✓ Saved confirmation appears at the bottom of the screen, and the update writes back to the Google Sheet automatically.

---

## Pipeline Status Values

| Status | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| **Prospect** | Identified but not yet contacted |
| **Contacted** | Initial outreach made |
| **In Discussion** | Active conversation underway |
| **Proposal Sent** | Formal proposal or partnership terms shared |
| **Active Partner** | Partnership confirmed and active |
| **On Hold** | Paused — revisit later |
| **Declined** | Not interested or not a fit |

