## Tips

- **Reload to sync** — if someone else updated the Sheet directly, reload the page to pull the latest data
- **Mobile friendly** — the app works on phones and tablets; use the bottom nav bar to switch views and the ☰ menu to access the full sidebar
- **Filters and search stack** — filter to Tier 1 first, then search within that filtered list
- **Funnel is clickable** — tap any bar on the dashboard to jump to that filtered pipeline view
- **Sort is persistent** — the sort direction stays active while you search and filter
- **Export respects filters** — if you filter to Tier 1 before exporting, only Tier 1 contacts download
- **✓ Saved toast** — after hitting Save Update, a green confirmation appears at the bottom confirming the Sheet was updated

